title: I made cartoon art cookies for Valentine’s Day (inspired by @cutepolish!)
description:
I love the look of these cartoon art cookies for Valentine's Day! 

To make them, I baked my chocolate cut-out cookie recipe in the shape of hearts and decorated them with flood consistency royal icing (my recipes are available in my book Cookie Canvas and in my Cookie Art Club https://sweetambs.mn.co!). 

I used Chefmaster food coloring to make black icing and two shades of each color. The thin black lines are drawn on with a FooDoodler edible ink marker. 

Let me know what you think of these cookies! 

Here's the video from @cutepolish that inspired these cookies: https://youtu.be/wpWrrZhluF0
